---
title: Easy Mumbai Beef Chuck & Coconut Curry with Garlic Rice & Coriander
description: Good things come to those who wait, and this meal is well worth the time put in. Hours in the slow cooker transform beef chuck into a meltingly tender delight, taking on the flavours of warm, aromatic spices and mild coconut milk. Trust us, tonight’s dinner is one you won’t forget.
